Azure does not provide built‑in policies that Explicitly audit SSH (22) from 0.0.0.0/0, Explicitly audit RDP (3389) from 0.0.0.0/0 Or *deny inbound Any:Any (0.0.0.0/0 → )

Correct Implementation Approach


Requirement			Policy Type
Deny inbound Any:Any		Custom Policy (Deny)
Audit SSH from Internet		Custom Policy (Audit)
Audit RDP from Internet		Custom Policy (Audit)

Implement (Portal – Step by Step)

1. Azure Portal → Policy
2. Definitions → Create
3. Paste each custom policy JSON
4. Save definitions
5. Assign policies at: Management Group or Subscription
6. Enforcement: Any:Any → Deny and SSH/RDP → Audit
